  ('kids-golf-camps-3-day-program-5yrs-8yrs-5', 'Kids Golf Camps '' 3-Day Program (5yrs - 8yrs)', 'Get your junior golfer out on the course and building skills this season! Our 3-day camps are designed to be fun, active, and educational, with a focus on developing the fundamentals of the game. Throughout the camp, we''ll cover: Full swing with irons and driver. Chipping and putting techniques. On-course experience playing a hole. Perfect for young golfers of all skill levels looking to learn, improve, and enjoy the game in a supportive environment. Time: 03:15 pm - 04:00 pm.', 'City of Yellowknife', 'Sports', 5, 8, 'Yellowknife', 'Parks, 4807 - 52 St', NULL, '2026-08-04', '2026-08-06', NULL, 'paid', 50, 'https://yellowknife.perfectmind.com/Contacts/BookMe4BookingPages/BookingCoursesPage?calendarId=be3ea5f4-ef36-101d-d685-729ff55fe6b0&widgetId=15f6af07-39c5-473e-b053-96653f77a406&embed=False', NULL, NULL, 'https://yellowknife.perfectmind.com/Contacts/BookMe4BookingPages/BookingCoursesPage?calendarId=be3ea5f4-ef36-101d-d685-729ff55fe6b0&widgetId=15f6af07-39c5-473e-b053-96653f77a406&embed=False', NULL, 'active', false),
