  ('great-slave-sailing-club-cansail-opti-wet-feet', 'Great Slave Sailing Club - CANSAIL Opti Wet Feet Course', 'A Summer 2026 two-week half-day beginner sailing program for children ages 5-7. Students learn sailing basics, water safety, movement and balance skills using Optimist dinghies, with recreational activities depending on wind and weather conditions. Use of club boats and clubhouse facilities is included. Runs Monday to Friday, 8:30 a.m.-12:00 p.m.; drop-off is after 8:15 a.m. and pickup is by 12:15 p.m. Cost is $395 + GST.', 'Great Slave Sailing Club', 'Sports', 5, 7, 'Yellowknife', 'Great Slave Sailing Club', 'Adjacent to the Giant Mine Boat Launch, old Highway 4 past the Ski Club, Yellowknife', '2026-06-01', '2026-08-31', NULL, 'paid', 395, 'https://greatslavesailingclub.checklick.com/', 'communications@greatslavesailingclub.com', NULL, 'https://greatslavesailingclub.checklick.com/', NULL, 'active', true),
